	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero te meas nuper ad te missas accepisse literas, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8432" cert="high">Frideryche</persName>, colendissime domine et frater charissime.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In his pleraque exposui, quae habui et quae tu in postremis ad me tuis 10. maii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l440" cert="high">Samadeni</placeName> datis scire postulabas.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Filius noster <persName ref="p6831" cert="high">Ioannes Traversus a Salicibus</persName> est <placeName ref="l21" cert="high">Badenae</placeName> et lavat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Superioribus diebus misi ad illum, ut scirem, et quid ageret et valeret, ac res omnis, deo gratia, erat in tuto.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rursus illum ad nos venturum brevi expectamus; intelligo enim illum nostri desiderio teneri, utcunque liberaliter foveatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gaudemus te post nundinas venturum ad nos ac hortamur te, ne sinas ullam remoram impedire tuam profectionem.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fama est hic quoque <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p17907" cert="high">Ferrandum Gonzagam</persName> descensurum ex Italia in Belgicum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie retulit mihi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglus</placeName> quidam medicus recta ascendens ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordia</placeName> literas esse ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> allatas significantes 10. maii in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgicum</placeName> ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> traiecisse <persName type="citizen_name">Philippum</persName> et parasse sibi militem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglum</placeName> et impetrasse pecuniam non exiguam contra Gallum.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego tamen hoc pro comperta veritate non asseveraverim; metuo tamen regem brevi plures habitur hostes quam velit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eo impulit illum papa, Antichristus sceleratissimus.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Urbes evangelicae 4 in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetia</placeName> mittent ad regem legationem pro Waldensibus in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemonte</placeName> supplicatum; nam hos per parlamentum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1291" cert="high">Taurinense</placeName> statuerat rex persequi.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt religionis nostrae.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioannem Fabricium</persName> <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiae</placeName> agentem tanquam me ipsum commendo iterum; commendo item amplissimum regis legatum d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p629">Mathaeum Cognetum</persName>, qui nuper missus est a rege in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rhetiam</placeName>; fratrum literis mihi commendatus est, ut qui syncerissimus sit in vera fide, regi quoque charissimus, et qui plura religionis in profectum egerit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta illum meo nomine diligentissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Colloquium celebrabitur 24. augusti <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l569" cert="high">Wormaciae</placeName> institutum ab ordinibus imperii evangelicis et papisticis; deputatus est praeses, designati assessores, colloqutores, notarii, adiuncti, supernumerarii, de quibus omnibus longum esset et molestum scribere.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reparata est tamen persequtio in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgico</placeName> contra fideles.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comicia erunt principum <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordiae</placeName> 18. iunii de rebus instituta variis.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germani</placeName> principes evangelici et ipsi mittent legatos cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiis</placeName> ad regem.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxones</placeName> quidam concionatores rursus in nos aediderunt libellos maledicos, acerbos et ineptissimos.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Singuli te salutant, quos salvere iusseras, inprimis autem d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyr</persName> et generi mei et reliquus chorus.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vive et vale una cum honestissima coniuge, tota domo tua et d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6831" cert="high">Traverso</persName>.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Iterum vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 21. maii 1557.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Insigni pietate et nobilitate claro viro d. <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Friderycho a Salice</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l440" cert="high">Rheto Samadeni</placeName> agenti, domino meo colendissimo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
